genresAdvancedInfo.name: tamil indie
genresAdvancedInfo.description: A genre of music that emerged from the independent music scene in Tamil Nadu, India. It is characterized by its experimental and eclectic sound, drawing inspiration from various genres such as rock, folk, and electronic music. Tamil indie often features socially conscious lyrics and a DIY ethos, with many artists self-producing and distributing their music.
